Desc     &WThis exhibition area is dedicated to the lost cities, kingdoms,
and special buildings that were once part of the material plane. 
A large stained glass window nearby depicts Qylaith watching
as various cities fall and disappear. Many models of what some of
these places looked like can be found here.
~
Perdesc  &wYou see further information next to the &Wmodels&w of dead cities.
~
